<h2>Keyboard Short-cuts</h2>


<p>
Quickplot has GUIs for all of the following immutable keyboard short-cuts:
</p>

<table summary="list of Quickplot key short-cuts" style="margin-bottom:0px;">

<tr><td><b>a</b></td> <td>show information <b><u>a</u></b>bout Quickplot using a web browser</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>b</b></td> <td>toggles the visibility of the <b><u>b</u></b>utton bar</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>c</b></td> <td><b><u>c</u></b>opies the current focused main window</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>d</b></td> <td><b><u>d</u></b>elete the main window. This will not close the last main window.</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>f</b></td> <td>toggles the visibility of the main border (<b><u>f</u></b>rame)</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>g</b></td> <td>show/hide the <b><u>g</u></b>raph configuration widget</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>h</b></td> <td>show <b><u>h</u></b>elp using a web browser</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>i</b></td> <td>save a PNG <b><u>i</u></b>mage of the graph</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>m</b></td> <td>show/hide the <b><u>m</u></b>enu bar</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>n</b></td> <td>make a <b><u>n</u></b>ew graph</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>o</b></td> <td><b><u>o</u></b>pen a data file</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>p</b></td> <td>show/hide the <b><u>p</u></b>lot lister widget</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>q</b></td> <td><b><u>q</u></b>uit</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>r</b></td> <td>toggles the between d<b><u>r</u></b>awing with Cairo and X11</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>s</b></td> <td>toggles the visibility of the <b><u>s</u></b>tatus bar</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>t</b></td> <td>toggles the visibility of the graph <b><u>t</u></b>abs</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>u</b></td> <td>toggles f<b><u>u</u></b>ll screen viewing</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>w</b></td> <td>makes a new main <b><u>w</u></b>indow</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>x</b></td><td>toggles the X11 shape e<b><u>x</u></b>tension on and off</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>z</b></td> <td><b><u>z</u></b>oom out one level</td</tr>
<tr><td><b>Z</b></td> <td><b><u>Z</u></b>oom out all the way</td</tr>
</table>

<table summary="The Rest of Quickplot key short-cuts" style="margin-top:0px;">
<tr><td style="white-space:nowrap;"><b>esc</b></td> <td>close the current focused window. This will not close the last main window.</td</tr>
<tr><td style="white-space:nowrap;"><b>left/right arrow</b></td>
  <td>the right and left arrow keys cycle though graph tabs when the buttons and tabs are not showing</td</tr>
</table>



